---
import Reveal from '../components/Reveal.astro';
---

<section id="light-lane" class="relative py-24">
	<div
		class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] items-start"
	>
		<Reveal class="space-y-6">
			<span
				class="badge badge-primary badge-outline text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase"
				>Light Lane</span
			>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white">
				Lightning-fast engraving software purpose-built for makers
			</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-200/85 leading-relaxed">
				Light Lane compresses everything from SVG import to engrave-ready
				streaming into a five-step, offline-first workflow. Every release ships
				with the same goal: fewer clicks, smarter defaults, and confidence
				before a single pulse fires.
			</p>
			<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
				<div class="glass p-6 space-y-3">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Core flow</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300/90 leading-relaxed">
						<li>
							• Intelligent import normalises layers, fonts, and vectors
							instantly.
						</li>
						<li>
							• GPU preview highlights pass order, collisions, and wasted
							travel.
						</li>
						<li>
							• Material guardrails auto-tune power & speed to stay
							production-safe.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="glass p-6 space-y-3">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">What makers love</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300/90 leading-relaxed">
						<li>
							• Driverless streaming to supported Ruida, GRBL, and G-code
							controllers.
						</li>
						<li>
							• Path optimiser merges travel to shave minutes off production
							runs.
						</li>
						<li>
							• Offline activation keeps shop-floor machines air-gapped but in
							sync.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
				<Reveal class="glass p-6" delay={80}>
					<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-quartz/70">
						Reusable templates
					</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-200/90 leading-relaxed">
						Drop in new artwork and Light Lane repositions, rescales, and
						restores presets instantly.
					</p>
				</Reveal>
				<Reveal class="glass p-6" delay={160}>
					<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-quartz/70">
						Multi-mode processing
					</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-200/90 leading-relaxed">
						Outline, shape, and raster modes auto-select the cleanest sequencing
						for detail fidelity.
					</p>
				</Reveal>
				<Reveal class="glass p-6" delay={240}>
					<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-quartz/70">
						Cross-platform parity
					</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-200/90 leading-relaxed">
						Native macOS & Windows builds share templates, materials, and
						analytics with no extra work.
					</p>
				</Reveal>
			</div>
		</Reveal>
		<Reveal class="glass p-8 lg:p-10 space-y-8">
			<div class="space-y-3">
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-quartz/70">
					Shop-floor wins
				</p>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
					From hobby bench to production line
				</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-200/85 leading-relaxed">
					Teams adopt Light Lane when they need predictable throughput: less
					setup time, cleaner motion paths, and the option to run fully offline
					without sacrificing analytics or templating.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-quartz/70">
					Highlights
				</p>
				<div class="grid gap-3">
					<span
						class="badge badge-lg badge-outline border-white/20 text-quartz/80"
						>Materials database</span
					>
					<span
						class="badge badge-lg badge-outline border-white/20 text-quartz/80"
						>Device-ready streaming</span
					>
					<span
						class="badge badge-lg badge-outline border-white/20 text-quartz/80"
						>Template marketplace</span
					>
					<span
						class="badge badge-lg badge-outline border-white/20 text-quartz/80"
						>Offline activation</span
					>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
				<a
					href="https://lightlane.app"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noreferrer"
					class="btn btn-secondary btn-wide rounded-full">Visit lightlane.app</a
				>
				<a
					href="#contact"
					class="btn btn-outline btn-wide rounded-full border-white/20 bg-white/5"
					>Launch with me</a
				>
			</div>
		</Reveal>
	</div>
</section>
